  [dialog 2/8]   |   "documents": [
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Coca-Cola. Coca-Cola is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. The classic refreshment.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Coca-Cola. Coca-Cola is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. The classic refreshment.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Hamburger. The original burger. A 100% beef patty seasoned with a pinch of salt and pepper, topped with tangy pickles, chopped onions, ketchup and mustard.. 100% beef patty, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. The classic that started it all.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Happy Meal (4pc McNuggets). A Happy Meal with 4 Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. 4pc Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A meal that makes kids smile.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Orange Juice. The McDonald's Minute Maid Orange Juice is 100% orange juice, loaded with Vitamin C. Available in small and medium sizes.. 100% orange juice from concentrate. Start your day with vitamin C.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Diet Coke. Small Diet Coke — crisp and refreshing.. Carbonated water, caramel color, aspartame, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. Zero-calorie cola.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Happy Meal (Hamburger). A Happy Meal with a Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A classic meal for kids.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "10pc Chicken McNuggets. Our tender, juicy Chicken McNuggets are made with 100% white meat chicken and no artificial colors, flavors or preservatives.. Chicken bites with tempura batter. The perfect shareable snack.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Diet Coke. Diet Coke with the same great taste and no calories.. Carbonated water, caramel color, aspartame, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. Zero-calorie cola.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Minute Maid Lemonade. Classic lemonade with real lemon flavor.. Water, high fructose corn syrup, lemon juice concentrate. Tart and refreshing.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Fanta Orange. Caffeine-free orange soda with a fruity burst.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors. Bright orange soda.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Black Coffee. Perfectly brewed for any time of the day.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Dr Pepper. Unique blend of 23 flavors in a bold fountain drink.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, natural and artificial flavors. 23 flavors in one drink.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Hash Browns. Our Hash Browns are deliciously tasty and perfectly crispy. These shredded potato hash brown patties are prepared so they're fluffy on the inside and crispy and toasty on the outside.. Shredded potatoes, salt, pepper, dextrose. Golden and crispy breakfast side.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Bottled Water. Refreshing purified drinking water.. Purified water. Hydration on the go.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Apple Slices. Fresh, crisp apple slices. A wholesome choice for any meal.. Fresh sliced apples. A fresh, healthy side.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Sweet Tea. Freshly brewed iced tea sweetened just right.. Brewed tea, sugar, water. Southern-style sweet tea.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Iced Tea. A blend of aromatic tea and the fruity flavour of lemon.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Side Salad. A fresh mix of greens including baby spinach, baby kale, lollo rossa, red leaf lettuce, red oak and red tango. Topped with grape tomatoes and shredded carrots.. Mixed greens, grape tomatoes, shredded carrots. Fresh greens on the side.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Sprite. Sprite is a delicious lemon-lime fountain drink and is available in extra small, small, medium, and large sizes.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors, sodium citrate, sodium benzoate. Crisp and refreshing.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Sprite. Sprite is a delicious lemon-lime fountain drink and is available in extra small, small, medium, and large sizes.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors, sodium citrate, sodium benzoate. Crisp and refreshing.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Premium Roast Coffee. Medium-roast coffee made from 100% Arabica beans — smooth and balanced.. 100% Arabica coffee, water. Freshly brewed every day.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Premium Roast Coffee. Small cup of medium-roast Arabica coffee.. 100% Arabica coffee, water. Freshly brewed every day."
  [dialog 2/8]   |   ]
  [dialog 2/8]   | }
