  [dialog 2/8]   |   "documents": [
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McFlurry (Choco Crunch). Milk-based frozen dessert with chocolate crispies and chocolate dip.. Milk fat, Chocolate. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McFlurry (Choco Crunch). Milk-based frozen dessert with chocolate crispies and chocolate dip.. Milk fat, Chocolate. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Veg Maharaja Mac. A double-decker toasted Maharaja bun sandwiched with one layer of corn & cheese patty; crunchy iceberg lettuce; shredded onion; and a slice of cheese. Topped with another layer of corn & cheese patty;\n                                tomato slices; and crunchy iceberg lettuce infused with harberno sauce.. Maharaja bun crown, Cocktail sauce, Shredded lettuce, Shredded onion, Jalepenos, Corn & cheese patty, club, Sliced cheese, Maharaja bun heel. A feast fit for kings (and queens).",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McFlurry (Oreo). Milk-based frozen dessert with oreo cookies.. Milk fat, Oreo. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McFlurry (Oreo). Milk-based frozen dessert with oreo cookies.. Milk fat, Oreo. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McChicken Biscuit. A crispy chicken fillet on a warm buttermilk biscuit brushed with real butter.. Crispy chicken patty, butter, buttermilk biscuit. Southern-style chicken on a biscuit.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Pizza McPuff. A blend of assorted vegetables (carrot, beans,capsicum, onion & green peas); mozzarella cheese mixed with tomato sauce; and exotic spices stuffed in rectangle shaped savoury dough. Quick frozen.. Assorted vegetables, Refined wheat flour, Pizza seasoning. Something different. Something delicious.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken Maharaja Mac. A double-decker toasted Maharaja bun sandwiched with one layer of flame-grilled chicken patty; crunchy iceberg lettuce; shredded onion; and a slice of cheese. Topped with another layer of flame-grilled\n                                chicken patty; tomato slices; and crunchy iceberg lettuce infused with harberno sauce.. Maharaja bun crown, Haberno sauce, Shredded lettuce, Shredded onion, Jalapenos, Flame-grilled chicken patty, Sliced cheese, Maharaja bun heel. A royal treat.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Veg Surprise Burger. A scrumptious potato patty topped with a delectable Italian herb sauce and shredded onions placed between perfectly toasted buns.. Regular Bun, Italian mayo, Shredded onion, Herb Chilli Potato patty. A surprise that will leave you wide-eyed.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McAloo Tikki Burger. A golden fried vegetarian patty prepared with peas, potato and infused with aromatic spices. Clubbed with sliced tomatoes, shredded red onion, and tangy tomato mayonnaise. Served in a warm toasted bun.. Regular bun crown, Tom-Mayo sauce, Sliced tomatoes, Shredded onion, Aloo tikki patty, Regular bun heel. The one that never goes out of f(l)avour.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Cheesy Fries. The all-time favourite fries with a generous dollop of cheesy yet smoky chipotle sauce.. Salted Fries, Smoky Chipotle Sauce. Hi, it’s cheese on this side!",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Cold Coffee Mcfloat. Rich smooth creamy cold coffee along with sweet vanilla flavoured soft serve mix.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McSpicy Paneer. Crispy and spicy paneer patty with creamy tandoori sauce and crispy lettuce topping.. Quarter pounder bun crown, Shredded lettuce, Tandoori mayo, Spicy paneer patty, Quarter pounder bun heel. Let paneer surprise you.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Black Coffee. Perfectly brewed for any time of the day.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Big Mac. Mouthwatering perfection starts with two 100% pure beef patties and Big Mac sauce sandwiched between a sesame seed bun. It's topped off with pickles, crisp shredded lettuce, finely chopped onion and American cheese.. Two 100% beef patties, Big Mac sauce, lettuce, cheese, pickles, onions, sesame seed bun. Two all-beef patties, special sauce, lettuce, cheese.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Happy Meal (4pc McNuggets). A Happy Meal with 4 Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. 4pc Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A meal that makes kids smile.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Bacon Egg Cheese Biscuit. Warm biscuit with crispy bacon, folded egg and American cheese.. Buttermilk biscuit, folded egg, bacon, American cheese. Hearty biscuit breakfast.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Dosa Masala Burger. Turmeric-spiced mashed potato filling topped with fresh peas. Grilled and placed inside a soft whole wheat bun with a spicy molagapodi chutney mayo.. Whole wheat bun, Rasam mayo, Dosa masala aloo patty. A new taste of India.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Sausage Biscuit with Egg. Savory sausage and fluffy folded egg on a buttermilk biscuit.. Buttermilk biscuit, sausage patty, folded egg. Portable breakfast sandwich.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McSpicy Chicken. Zesty and redolent whole muscle leg meat patty: Fried to perfect golden tan; quenched with creamy veg mayo and garden-fresh shredded iceberg lettuce. The sandwich is served in fresh, sesame-studded quarter\n                                pounder bun.. Quarter pounder bun crown, Veg sauce, Shredded lettuce, McSpicy chicken patty, Quarter pounder bun heel. Hot. In more ways than one.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McEgg. Made with the freshest, warm, off-the-farm egg; steamed to perfection in our specialised steamer; and made tasty with a sprinkling of magic masala. Sandwiched between freshly toasted buns, topped off with\n                                creamy mayo and some crunchy onion.. Regular bun crown, Mayonnaise, Crisp onion, Egg, Curry spices, Regular bun heel. Because eggs are great any time of the day.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Sausage McMuffin. A savory sausage patty and melty American cheese on a toasted English muffin.. English muffin, sausage patty, American cheese. Simple morning classic.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Spicy Crispy Chicken Sandwich. A southern style fried chicken sandwich with a spicy pepper sauce. It's crispy, juicy, tender and topped with crinkle-cut pickles on a toasted, buttered potato roll.. Spicy crispy chicken fillet, crinkle-cut pickles, spicy pepper sauce, potato roll. Crispy chicken with a kick.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Caramel Macchiato. Freshly steamed milk with vanilla-flavored syrup marked with espresso and caramel drizzle.. Espresso, steamed milk, vanilla syrup, caramel drizzle. Layered espresso favorite.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McSwirl Chocolate. Delightful soft-serve with a delectable chocolate topping.. Soft serve mix (100% diary product), Chocolate dip. Melts in your mouth. Goes to your heart.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Crispy Chicken Sandwich. A southern style fried chicken sandwich that's crispy, juicy and tender perfection. It's topped with crinkle-cut pickles and served on a toasted, buttered potato roll.. Crispy chicken fillet, crinkle-cut pickles, butter, potato roll. Crispy, juicy, tender.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "McChicken. Batter & breaded chicken patty containing green peas, carrots, green beans, onion, potatoes, rice and spices, served in a bun with eggless mayonnaise and lettuce.. Quarter bun crown, Veg mayonnaise, Shredded lettuce, McChicken patty, Quarter bun heel. Familiarity breeds confidence.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Vanilla Shake. Classic vanilla shake — smooth and sweet.. Vanilla soft serve, milk. Simple vanilla bliss.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Soft Serve Cone. Creamy vanilla soft-serve on a cone.. Soft serve mix (100% diary product). Delightfully basic.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Sundae (Strawberry). Creamy vanilla soft-serve with strawberry topping.. Soft serve mix (100% diary), Strawberry topping. A little zing goes a long way.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Sundae (Strawberry). Creamy vanilla soft-serve with strawberry topping.. Soft serve mix (100% diary), Strawberry topping. A little zing goes a long way.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Coca-Cola. Coca-Cola is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. The classic refreshment.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Coca-Cola. Coca-Cola is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. The classic refreshment.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Orange Juice. The McDonald's Minute Maid Orange Juice is 100% orange juice, loaded with Vitamin C. Available in small and medium sizes.. 100% orange juice from concentrate. Start your day with vitamin C.",
  [dialog 2/8]   |     "Minute Maid Lemonade. Classic lemonade with real lemon flavor.. Water, high fructose corn syrup, lemon juice concentrate. Tart and refreshing."
  [dialog 2/8]   |   ]
  [dialog 2/8]   | }
