  [dialog 1/8]   |   "documents": [
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McChicken. Batter & breaded chicken patty containing green peas, carrots, green beans, onion, potatoes, rice and spices, served in a bun with eggless mayonnaise and lettuce.. Quarter bun crown, Veg mayonnaise, Shredded lettuce, McChicken patty, Quarter bun heel. Familiarity breeds confidence.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McChicken Biscuit. A crispy chicken fillet on a warm buttermilk biscuit brushed with real butter.. Crispy chicken patty, butter, buttermilk biscuit. Southern-style chicken on a biscuit.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McFlurry (Choco Crunch). Milk-based frozen dessert with chocolate crispies and chocolate dip.. Milk fat, Chocolate. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McFlurry (Choco Crunch). Milk-based frozen dessert with chocolate crispies and chocolate dip.. Milk fat, Chocolate. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McSpicy Paneer. Crispy and spicy paneer patty with creamy tandoori sauce and crispy lettuce topping.. Quarter pounder bun crown, Shredded lettuce, Tandoori mayo, Spicy paneer patty, Quarter pounder bun heel. Let paneer surprise you.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Hamburger. The original burger. A 100% beef patty seasoned with a pinch of salt and pepper, topped with tangy pickles, chopped onions, ketchup and mustard.. 100% beef patty, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. The classic that started it all.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McSpicy Chicken. Zesty and redolent whole muscle leg meat patty: Fried to perfect golden tan; quenched with creamy veg mayo and garden-fresh shredded iceberg lettuce. The sandwich is served in fresh, sesame-studded quarter\n                                pounder bun.. Quarter pounder bun crown, Veg sauce, Shredded lettuce, McSpicy chicken patty, Quarter pounder bun heel. Hot. In more ways than one.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McVeggie. A delectable patty made of green goodness, potatoes, peas, carrots and a selection of Indian spices. Topped with crispy lettuce, mayonnaise, and packed into sesame toasted buns.. Quarter bun crown, Veg mayonnaise, Shredded lettuce, Vegetable patty, Quarter bun heel. Pure taste. Pure veg.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Happy Meal (4pc McNuggets). A Happy Meal with 4 Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. 4pc Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A meal that makes kids smile.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Chicken Maharaja Mac. A double-decker toasted Maharaja bun sandwiched with one layer of flame-grilled chicken patty; crunchy iceberg lettuce; shredded onion; and a slice of cheese. Topped with another layer of flame-grilled\n                                chicken patty; tomato slices; and crunchy iceberg lettuce infused with harberno sauce.. Maharaja bun crown, Haberno sauce, Shredded lettuce, Shredded onion, Jalapenos, Flame-grilled chicken patty, Sliced cheese, Maharaja bun heel. A royal treat.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McDouble. The McDouble features two 100% pure beef patties seasoned with just a pinch of salt and pepper. It's topped with tangy pickles, chopped onions, ketchup, mustard and a slice of melty American cheese.. Two 100% beef patties, one slice of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. Double the beef, double the taste.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Cheesy Fries. The all-time favourite fries with a generous dollop of cheesy yet smoky chipotle sauce.. Salted Fries, Smoky Chipotle Sauce. Hi, it’s cheese on this side!",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McAloo Tikki Burger. A golden fried vegetarian patty prepared with peas, potato and infused with aromatic spices. Clubbed with sliced tomatoes, shredded red onion, and tangy tomato mayonnaise. Served in a warm toasted bun.. Regular bun crown, Tom-Mayo sauce, Sliced tomatoes, Shredded onion, Aloo tikki patty, Regular bun heel. The one that never goes out of f(l)avour.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Big Mac. Mouthwatering perfection starts with two 100% pure beef patties and Big Mac sauce sandwiched between a sesame seed bun. It's topped off with pickles, crisp shredded lettuce, finely chopped onion and American cheese.. Two 100% beef patties, Big Mac sauce, lettuce, cheese, pickles, onions, sesame seed bun. Two all-beef patties, special sauce, lettuce, cheese.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McFlurry (Oreo). Milk-based frozen dessert with oreo cookies.. Milk fat, Oreo. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "McFlurry (Oreo). Milk-based frozen dessert with oreo cookies.. Milk fat, Oreo. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Pizza McPuff. A blend of assorted vegetables (carrot, beans,capsicum, onion & green peas); mozzarella cheese mixed with tomato sauce; and exotic spices stuffed in rectangle shaped savoury dough. Quick frozen.. Assorted vegetables, Refined wheat flour, Pizza seasoning. Something different. Something delicious.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Cheeseburger. Our simple, classic cheeseburger begins with a 100% pure beef patty seasoned with just a pinch of salt and pepper. It's topped with a tangy pickle, chopped onions, ketchup, mustard, and a slice of melty American cheese.. 100% beef patty, one slice of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. A timeless classic with cheese.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Crispy Chicken Sandwich. A southern style fried chicken sandwich that's crispy, juicy and tender perfection. It's topped with crinkle-cut pickles and served on a toasted, buttered potato roll.. Crispy chicken fillet, crinkle-cut pickles, butter, potato roll. Crispy, juicy, tender.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Double Cheeseburger. The Double Cheeseburger features two 100% pure beef patties seasoned with just a pinch of salt and pepper. It's topped with tangy pickles, chopped onions, ketchup, mustard and two slices of melty American cheese.. Two 100% beef patties, two slices of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. Twice the cheese, twice the flavor.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Double Quarter Pounder with Cheese. Two quarter pound 100% beef patties with two slices of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup and mustard on a sesame seed bun.. Two quarter pound beef patties, two cheese slices, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, sesame bun. Serious beef appetite.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Spicy Paneer Wrap. Tender paneer patty with a fiery, crunchy batter coating; dressed with fresh veggies and seasonings; topped with creamy sauce; and a dash of mustard and melted cheese.. Whole wheat flat bread, Spicy paneer patty, Veg mayo, Lettuce, Onion, Tomato, Mustard sauce, Cheese. Unwrap deliciousness.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Spicy Crispy Chicken Sandwich. A southern style fried chicken sandwich with a spicy pepper sauce. It's crispy, juicy, tender and topped with crinkle-cut pickles on a toasted, buttered potato roll.. Spicy crispy chicken fillet, crinkle-cut pickles, spicy pepper sauce, potato roll. Crispy chicken with a kick.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Happy Meal (Hamburger). A Happy Meal with a Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A classic meal for kids.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Butter Paneer Grilled Burger. Mildly spiced grilled paneer patty topped with makhani sauce and shredded onions placed between freshly toasted sesame seeded buns.. Mildly spiced grilled paneer patty, Shredded onion, Sesame seeded buns. Dil se makhani burger.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Veg Maharaja Mac. A double-decker toasted Maharaja bun sandwiched with one layer of corn & cheese patty; crunchy iceberg lettuce; shredded onion; and a slice of cheese. Topped with another layer of corn & cheese patty;\n                                tomato slices; and crunchy iceberg lettuce infused with harberno sauce.. Maharaja bun crown, Cocktail sauce, Shredded lettuce, Shredded onion, Jalepenos, Corn & cheese patty, club, Sliced cheese, Maharaja bun heel. A feast fit for kings (and queens).",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Hash Browns. Our Hash Browns are deliciously tasty and perfectly crispy. These shredded potato hash brown patties are prepared so they're fluffy on the inside and crispy and toasty on the outside.. Shredded potatoes, salt, pepper, dextrose. Golden and crispy breakfast side.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Butter Chicken Grilled Burger. Premium grilled chicken patty topped with makhani sauce and shredded onions placed between freshly toasted sesame seeded buns.. Premium grilled chicken patty, Shredded onion, Sesame seeded buns. Dil se makhani burger.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Quarter Pounder Deluxe. Quarter pound beef with cheese, shredded lettuce, tomato, mayo, pickles and slivered onions on a sesame seed bun.. Quarter pound beef patty, cheese, lettuce, tomato, mayo, pickles, onions, sesame bun. Fresh veggies on a quarter pounder.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Apple Pie. McDonald's Baked Apple Pie features 100% American-grown apples, and a lattice crust baked to perfection and topped with sprinkled sugar.. Apples, flour, sugar, palm oil, cinnamon, salt. A warm, sweet classic.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Bacon Quarter Pounder with Cheese. A quarter pound of 100% beef with thick-cut applewood smoked bacon, two slices of cheese, pickles, ketchup and mustard.. Quarter pound beef patty, bacon strips, cheese, pickles, ketchup, mustard, sesame bun. Smoky bacon meets quarter pound beef.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "10pc Chicken McNuggets. Our tender, juicy Chicken McNuggets are made with 100% white meat chicken and no artificial colors, flavors or preservatives.. Chicken bites with tempura batter. The perfect shareable snack.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Spicy Chicken Wrap. Juicy chicken coated with hot and crispy batter; dressed with a fresh salad of lettuce, onions, tomatoes and seasonings. Served with creamy sauce and supple cheese slices.. Whole wheat flat bread, Spicy chicken patty, Veg mayo, Lettuce, Onion, Tomato, Cheese. Familiar, yet different.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Veg Surprise Burger. A scrumptious potato patty topped with a delectable Italian herb sauce and shredded onions placed between perfectly toasted buns.. Regular Bun, Italian mayo, Shredded onion, Herb Chilli Potato patty. A surprise that will leave you wide-eyed.",
  [dialog 1/8]   |     "Caesar Salad with Grilled Chicken. Crisp romaine with grilled chicken, shaved parmesan, croutons and Caesar dressing.. Romaine lettuce, grilled chicken, parmesan, croutons, Caesar dressing. Lighter meal option."
  [dialog 1/8]   |   ]
