  [dialog 4/8]   |   "documents": [
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Butter Chicken Grilled Burger. Premium grilled chicken patty topped with makhani sauce and shredded onions placed between freshly toasted sesame seeded buns.. Premium grilled chicken patty, Shredded onion, Sesame seeded buns. Dil se makhani burger.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Crispy Chicken Sandwich. A southern style fried chicken sandwich that's crispy, juicy and tender perfection. It's topped with crinkle-cut pickles and served on a toasted, buttered potato roll.. Crispy chicken fillet, crinkle-cut pickles, butter, potato roll. Crispy, juicy, tender.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "McSpicy Chicken. Zesty and redolent whole muscle leg meat patty: Fried to perfect golden tan; quenched with creamy veg mayo and garden-fresh shredded iceberg lettuce. The sandwich is served in fresh, sesame-studded quarter\n                                pounder bun.. Quarter pounder bun crown, Veg sauce, Shredded lettuce, McSpicy chicken patty, Quarter pounder bun heel. Hot. In more ways than one.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Spicy Crispy Chicken Sandwich. A southern style fried chicken sandwich with a spicy pepper sauce. It's crispy, juicy, tender and topped with crinkle-cut pickles on a toasted, buttered potato roll.. Spicy crispy chicken fillet, crinkle-cut pickles, spicy pepper sauce, potato roll. Crispy chicken with a kick.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Spicy Chicken Wrap. Juicy chicken coated with hot and crispy batter; dressed with a fresh salad of lettuce, onions, tomatoes and seasonings. Served with creamy sauce and supple cheese slices.. Whole wheat flat bread, Spicy chicken patty, Veg mayo, Lettuce, Onion, Tomato, Cheese. Familiar, yet different.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "McChicken Biscuit. A crispy chicken fillet on a warm buttermilk biscuit brushed with real butter.. Crispy chicken patty, butter, buttermilk biscuit. Southern-style chicken on a biscuit.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Chicken Maharaja Mac. A double-decker toasted Maharaja bun sandwiched with one layer of flame-grilled chicken patty; crunchy iceberg lettuce; shredded onion; and a slice of cheese. Topped with another layer of flame-grilled\n                                chicken patty; tomato slices; and crunchy iceberg lettuce infused with harberno sauce.. Maharaja bun crown, Haberno sauce, Shredded lettuce, Shredded onion, Jalapenos, Flame-grilled chicken patty, Sliced cheese, Maharaja bun heel. A royal treat.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Caesar Salad with Grilled Chicken. Crisp romaine with grilled chicken, shaved parmesan, croutons and Caesar dressing.. Romaine lettuce, grilled chicken, parmesan, croutons, Caesar dressing. Lighter meal option.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Buttermilk Crispy Chicken Tenders. Three or four crispy all-white meat chicken tenders with a tangy dipping sauce.. Chicken breast strips, buttermilk batter, seasoned flour. Hand-breaded crispy strips.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Butter Paneer Grilled Burger. Mildly spiced grilled paneer patty topped with makhani sauce and shredded onions placed between freshly toasted sesame seeded buns.. Mildly spiced grilled paneer patty, Shredded onion, Sesame seeded buns. Dil se makhani burger.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Side Caesar Salad. Side portion Caesar salad without chicken.. Romaine lettuce, parmesan, croutons, Caesar dressing. Small salad side.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "10pc Chicken McNuggets. Our tender, juicy Chicken McNuggets are made with 100% white meat chicken and no artificial colors, flavors or preservatives.. Chicken bites with tempura batter. The perfect shareable snack.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Spicy Paneer Wrap. Tender paneer patty with a fiery, crunchy batter coating; dressed with fresh veggies and seasonings; topped with creamy sauce; and a dash of mustard and melted cheese.. Whole wheat flat bread, Spicy paneer patty, Veg mayo, Lettuce, Onion, Tomato, Mustard sauce, Cheese. Unwrap deliciousness.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "McChicken. Batter & breaded chicken patty containing green peas, carrots, green beans, onion, potatoes, rice and spices, served in a bun with eggless mayonnaise and lettuce.. Quarter bun crown, Veg mayonnaise, Shredded lettuce, McChicken patty, Quarter bun heel. Familiarity breeds confidence.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "McSpicy Paneer. Crispy and spicy paneer patty with creamy tandoori sauce and crispy lettuce topping.. Quarter pounder bun crown, Shredded lettuce, Tandoori mayo, Spicy paneer patty, Quarter pounder bun heel. Let paneer surprise you.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Double Quarter Pounder with Cheese. Two quarter pound 100% beef patties with two slices of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup and mustard on a sesame seed bun.. Two quarter pound beef patties, two cheese slices, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, sesame bun. Serious beef appetite.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "McVeggie. A delectable patty made of green goodness, potatoes, peas, carrots and a selection of Indian spices. Topped with crispy lettuce, mayonnaise, and packed into sesame toasted buns.. Quarter bun crown, Veg mayonnaise, Shredded lettuce, Vegetable patty, Quarter bun heel. Pure taste. Pure veg.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "McEgg. Made with the freshest, warm, off-the-farm egg; steamed to perfection in our specialised steamer; and made tasty with a sprinkling of magic masala. Sandwiched between freshly toasted buns, topped off with\n                                creamy mayo and some crunchy onion.. Regular bun crown, Mayonnaise, Crisp onion, Egg, Curry spices, Regular bun heel. Because eggs are great any time of the day.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "McAloo Tikki Burger. A golden fried vegetarian patty prepared with peas, potato and infused with aromatic spices. Clubbed with sliced tomatoes, shredded red onion, and tangy tomato mayonnaise. Served in a warm toasted bun.. Regular bun crown, Tom-Mayo sauce, Sliced tomatoes, Shredded onion, Aloo tikki patty, Regular bun heel. The one that never goes out of f(l)avour.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Hamburger. The original burger. A 100% beef patty seasoned with a pinch of salt and pepper, topped with tangy pickles, chopped onions, ketchup and mustard.. 100% beef patty, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. The classic that started it all.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Quarter Pounder Deluxe. Quarter pound beef with cheese, shredded lettuce, tomato, mayo, pickles and slivered onions on a sesame seed bun.. Quarter pound beef patty, cheese, lettuce, tomato, mayo, pickles, onions, sesame bun. Fresh veggies on a quarter pounder.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Happy Meal (4pc McNuggets). A Happy Meal with 4 Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. 4pc Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A meal that makes kids smile.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Quarter Pounder with Cheese. Each Quarter Pounder with Cheese burger features a quarter pound of 100% fresh beef that's hot, deliciously juicy and cooked when you order. It's seasoned with just a pinch of salt and pepper, sizzled on a flat iron grill, then topped with slivered onions, tangy pickles and two slices of melty American cheese on a sesame seed bun.. Quarter pound 100% beef patty, two slices of cheese, onions, pickles, mustard, ketchup, sesame seed bun. A quarter pound of 100% fresh beef.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Side Salad. A fresh mix of greens including baby spinach, baby kale, lollo rossa, red leaf lettuce, red oak and red tango. Topped with grape tomatoes and shredded carrots.. Mixed greens, grape tomatoes, shredded carrots. Fresh greens on the side.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "McDouble. The McDouble features two 100% pure beef patties seasoned with just a pinch of salt and pepper. It's topped with tangy pickles, chopped onions, ketchup, mustard and a slice of melty American cheese.. Two 100% beef patties, one slice of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. Double the beef, double the taste.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Bacon Quarter Pounder with Cheese. A quarter pound of 100% beef with thick-cut applewood smoked bacon, two slices of cheese, pickles, ketchup and mustard.. Quarter pound beef patty, bacon strips, cheese, pickles, ketchup, mustard, sesame bun. Smoky bacon meets quarter pound beef.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Sausage Biscuit with Egg. Savory sausage and fluffy folded egg on a buttermilk biscuit.. Buttermilk biscuit, sausage patty, folded egg. Portable breakfast sandwich.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Mozzarella Sticks. Breaded mozzarella sticks served with marinara sauce for dipping.. Mozzarella cheese, breading, marinara dipping sauce. Cheesy fried snack.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Double Cheeseburger. The Double Cheeseburger features two 100% pure beef patties seasoned with just a pinch of salt and pepper. It's topped with tangy pickles, chopped onions, ketchup, mustard and two slices of melty American cheese.. Two 100% beef patties, two slices of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. Twice the cheese, twice the flavor.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Big Mac. Mouthwatering perfection starts with two 100% pure beef patties and Big Mac sauce sandwiched between a sesame seed bun. It's topped off with pickles, crisp shredded lettuce, finely chopped onion and American cheese.. Two 100% beef patties, Big Mac sauce, lettuce, cheese, pickles, onions, sesame seed bun. Two all-beef patties, special sauce, lettuce, cheese.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Cheeseburger. Our simple, classic cheeseburger begins with a 100% pure beef patty seasoned with just a pinch of salt and pepper. It's topped with a tangy pickle, chopped onions, ketchup, mustard, and a slice of melty American cheese.. 100% beef patty, one slice of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, regular bun. A timeless classic with cheese.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Veg Surprise Burger. A scrumptious potato patty topped with a delectable Italian herb sauce and shredded onions placed between perfectly toasted buns.. Regular Bun, Italian mayo, Shredded onion, Herb Chilli Potato patty. A surprise that will leave you wide-eyed.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Veg Maharaja Mac. A double-decker toasted Maharaja bun sandwiched with one layer of corn & cheese patty; crunchy iceberg lettuce; shredded onion; and a slice of cheese. Topped with another layer of corn & cheese patty;\n                                tomato slices; and crunchy iceberg lettuce infused with harberno sauce.. Maharaja bun crown, Cocktail sauce, Shredded lettuce, Shredded onion, Jalepenos, Corn & cheese patty, club, Sliced cheese, Maharaja bun heel. A feast fit for kings (and queens).",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Cheesy Fries. The all-time favourite fries with a generous dollop of cheesy yet smoky chipotle sauce.. Salted Fries, Smoky Chipotle Sauce. Hi, it’s cheese on this side!",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Bacon Egg Cheese Biscuit. Warm biscuit with crispy bacon, folded egg and American cheese.. Buttermilk biscuit, folded egg, bacon, American cheese. Hearty biscuit breakfast.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Chocolate Brownie. Warm chocolate brownie with a fudgy center.. Flour, sugar, cocoa, eggs, butter, chocolate chips. Rich fudgy square.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Happy Meal (Hamburger). A Happy Meal with a Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A classic meal for kids.",
  [dialog 4/8]   |     "Dosa Masala Burger. Turmeric-spiced mashed potato filling topped with fresh peas. Grilled and placed inside a soft whole wheat bun with a spicy molagapodi chutney mayo.. Whole wheat bun, Rasam mayo, Dosa masala aloo patty. A new taste of India."
  [dialog 4/8]   |   ]
  [dialog 4/8]   | }
