  [dialog 6/8]   |   "documents": [
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Diet Coke. Small Diet Coke — crisp and refreshing.. Carbonated water, caramel color, aspartame, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. Zero-calorie cola.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Coca-Cola. Coca-Cola is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. The classic refreshment.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Coca-Cola. Coca-Cola is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. The classic refreshment.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Diet Coke. Diet Coke with the same great taste and no calories.. Carbonated water, caramel color, aspartame, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. Zero-calorie cola.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Fanta Orange. Caffeine-free orange soda with a fruity burst.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors. Bright orange soda.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sprite. Sprite is a delicious lemon-lime fountain drink and is available in extra small, small, medium, and large sizes.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors, sodium citrate, sodium benzoate. Crisp and refreshing.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sprite. Sprite is a delicious lemon-lime fountain drink and is available in extra small, small, medium, and large sizes.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors, sodium citrate, sodium benzoate. Crisp and refreshing.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Milk. 1% Low Fat Milk Jug is a wholesome drink choice for your Happy Meal.. Reduced fat milk, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D3. A wholesome drink choice.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Minute Maid Lemonade. Classic lemonade with real lemon flavor.. Water, high fructose corn syrup, lemon juice concentrate. Tart and refreshing.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Caramel Frappe. Blended coffee drink with buttery caramel and whipped cream.. Coffee, caramel syrup, ice, whipped cream, milk. Sweet frozen coffee.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Bottled Water. Refreshing purified drinking water.. Purified water. Hydration on the go.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Dr Pepper. Unique blend of 23 flavors in a bold fountain drink.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, natural and artificial flavors. 23 flavors in one drink.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Chocolate Milk. Fat Free Chocolate Milk Jug is a sweet treat for your Happy Meal.. Reduced fat milk, sugar, cocoa, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D3. A sweet treat in a jug.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McFlurry (Choco Crunch). Milk-based frozen dessert with chocolate crispies and chocolate dip.. Milk fat, Chocolate. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McFlurry (Choco Crunch). Milk-based frozen dessert with chocolate crispies and chocolate dip.. Milk fat, Chocolate. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Mango Pineapple Smoothie. Tropical mango and pineapple blended with yogurt.. Mango puree, pineapple juice, low-fat yogurt, ice. Tropical fruit blend.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sweet Tea. Freshly brewed iced tea sweetened just right.. Brewed tea, sugar, water. Southern-style sweet tea.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Iced Coffee. Chilled premium roast coffee with cream and a touch of sweetness.. Coffee, cream, liquid sugar. Cold and creamy pick-me-up.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Orange Juice. The McDonald's Minute Maid Orange Juice is 100% orange juice, loaded with Vitamin C. Available in small and medium sizes.. 100% orange juice from concentrate. Start your day with vitamin C.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Fruit and Yogurt Parfait. Our creamy, low-fat vanilla yogurt layered with strawberries, blueberries and crunchy granola. A delicious snack or treat.. Low-fat vanilla yogurt, strawberries, blueberries, granola. A fresh, fruity treat.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Iced Tea. A blend of aromatic tea and the fruity flavour of lemon.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Cold Coffee. A rich smooth creamy cold coffee made with coffee powder and milk.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "French Vanilla Latte. Rich espresso with steamed milk and French vanilla flavor.. Espresso, steamed milk, vanilla syrup. Sweet vanilla espresso drink.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McFlurry (Oreo). Milk-based frozen dessert with oreo cookies.. Milk fat, Oreo. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McFlurry (Oreo). Milk-based frozen dessert with oreo cookies.. Milk fat, Oreo. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Big Mac. Mouthwatering perfection starts with two 100% pure beef patties and Big Mac sauce sandwiched between a sesame seed bun. It's topped off with pickles, crisp shredded lettuce, finely chopped onion and American cheese.. Two 100% beef patties, Big Mac sauce, lettuce, cheese, pickles, onions, sesame seed bun. Two all-beef patties, special sauce, lettuce, cheese.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Strawberry Banana Smoothie. Blended strawberry and banana with creamy yogurt.. Strawberry puree, banana puree, low-fat yogurt, ice. Fruit smoothie treat.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Strawberry Shake. Strawberry-flavored shake blended with vanilla soft serve.. Vanilla soft serve, strawberry syrup, milk. Fruity pink shake.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Mocha Frappe. Mocha coffee frappe blended with ice and topped with whipped cream.. Coffee, mocha sauce, ice, whipped cream, milk. Frozen chocolate coffee treat.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Black Coffee. Perfectly brewed for any time of the day.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Chocolate Brownie. Warm chocolate brownie with a fudgy center.. Flour, sugar, cocoa, eggs, butter, chocolate chips. Rich fudgy square.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Pizza McPuff. A blend of assorted vegetables (carrot, beans,capsicum, onion & green peas); mozzarella cheese mixed with tomato sauce; and exotic spices stuffed in rectangle shaped savoury dough. Quick frozen.. Assorted vegetables, Refined wheat flour, Pizza seasoning. Something different. Something delicious.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Vanilla Shake. Classic vanilla shake — smooth and sweet.. Vanilla soft serve, milk. Simple vanilla bliss.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Chocolate Shake. Creamy chocolate shake made with vanilla soft serve and chocolate syrup.. Vanilla soft serve, chocolate syrup, milk. Thick and creamy classic.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Caramel Macchiato. Freshly steamed milk with vanilla-flavored syrup marked with espresso and caramel drizzle.. Espresso, steamed milk, vanilla syrup, caramel drizzle. Layered espresso favorite.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Hot Chocolate. Steamed milk with rich chocolate syrup and optional whipped topping.. Steamed milk, chocolate syrup, whipped cream. Warm chocolate comfort.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Cold Coffee Mcfloat. Rich smooth creamy cold coffee along with sweet vanilla flavoured soft serve mix.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Happy Meal (Hamburger). A Happy Meal with a Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A classic meal for kids.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Quarter Pounder Deluxe. Quarter pound beef with cheese, shredded lettuce, tomato, mayo, pickles and slivered onions on a sesame seed bun.. Quarter pound beef patty, cheese, lettuce, tomato, mayo, pickles, onions, sesame bun. Fresh veggies on a quarter pounder."
  [dialog 6/8]   |   ]
