  [dialog 3/8]   |       "role": "assistant",
  [dialog 3/8]   |       "content": "Big Mac: Mouthwatering perfection starts with two 100% pure beef patties and Big Mac sauce sandwiched between a sesame seed bun. It's topped off with pickles, crisp shredded lettuce, finely chopped onion and American cheese. Ingredients: Two 100% beef patties, Big Mac sauce, lettuce, cheese, pickles, onions, sesame seed bun. Allergens: Cereal containing gluten, Milk, Sesame. Approx. 550 kcal. Would you like to add it to your order?"
  [dialog 3/8]   |     },
  [dialog 3/8]   |     {
  [dialog 3/8]   |       "role": "user",
  [dialog 3/8]   |       "content": "Yeah, that's right."
  [dialog 3/8]   |     },
  [dialog 3/8]   |     {
  [dialog 3/8]   |       "role": "assistant",
  [dialog 3/8]   |       "content": "Alright, that’s a Big Mac, one McChicken for you, one McChicken for your child, and large fries with Coke for both. Does that sound right?"
  [dialog 3/8]   |     },
  [dialog 3/8]   |     {
  [dialog 3/8]   |       "role": "user",
  [dialog 3/8]   |       "content": "Yeah, that's all, thanks."
  [dialog 3/8]   |     }
  [dialog 3/8]   |   ],
  [dialog 3/8]   |   "response": "Got it! One Big Mac, one McChicken, large fries, and Coke for both. Your order is on the way."
