  [dialog 6/8]   |   "documents": [
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Bottled Water. Refreshing purified drinking water.. Purified water. Hydration on the go.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Happy Meal (Hamburger). A Happy Meal with a Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. Hamburger, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A classic meal for kids.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Chocolate Milk. Fat Free Chocolate Milk Jug is a sweet treat for your Happy Meal.. Reduced fat milk, sugar, cocoa, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D3. A sweet treat in a jug.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Happy Meal (4pc McNuggets). A Happy Meal with 4 Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, and your choice of a drink. Includes a fun toy!. 4pc Chicken McNuggets, small fries, apple slices, choice of drink. A meal that makes kids smile.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Milk. 1% Low Fat Milk Jug is a wholesome drink choice for your Happy Meal.. Reduced fat milk, vitamin A palmitate, vitamin D3. A wholesome drink choice.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McSwirl Chocolate. Delightful soft-serve with a delectable chocolate topping.. Soft serve mix (100% diary product), Chocolate dip. Melts in your mouth. Goes to your heart.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Side Salad. A fresh mix of greens including baby spinach, baby kale, lollo rossa, red leaf lettuce, red oak and red tango. Topped with grape tomatoes and shredded carrots.. Mixed greens, grape tomatoes, shredded carrots. Fresh greens on the side.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McFlurry (Choco Crunch). Milk-based frozen dessert with chocolate crispies and chocolate dip.. Milk fat, Chocolate. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McFlurry (Choco Crunch). Milk-based frozen dessert with chocolate crispies and chocolate dip.. Milk fat, Chocolate. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Fanta Orange. Caffeine-free orange soda with a fruity burst.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors. Bright orange soda.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McFlurry (Oreo). Milk-based frozen dessert with oreo cookies.. Milk fat, Oreo. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McFlurry (Oreo). Milk-based frozen dessert with oreo cookies.. Milk fat, Oreo. Burgers aren't the only things we're good at.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Chocolate Brownie. Warm chocolate brownie with a fudgy center.. Flour, sugar, cocoa, eggs, butter, chocolate chips. Rich fudgy square.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Cheesy Fries. The all-time favourite fries with a generous dollop of cheesy yet smoky chipotle sauce.. Salted Fries, Smoky Chipotle Sauce. Hi, it’s cheese on this side!",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Hot Chocolate. Steamed milk with rich chocolate syrup and optional whipped topping.. Steamed milk, chocolate syrup, whipped cream. Warm chocolate comfort.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sprite. Sprite is a delicious lemon-lime fountain drink and is available in extra small, small, medium, and large sizes.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors, sodium citrate, sodium benzoate. Crisp and refreshing.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sprite. Sprite is a delicious lemon-lime fountain drink and is available in extra small, small, medium, and large sizes.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, citric acid, natural flavors, sodium citrate, sodium benzoate. Crisp and refreshing.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McAloo Tikki Burger. A golden fried vegetarian patty prepared with peas, potato and infused with aromatic spices. Clubbed with sliced tomatoes, shredded red onion, and tangy tomato mayonnaise. Served in a warm toasted bun.. Regular bun crown, Tom-Mayo sauce, Sliced tomatoes, Shredded onion, Aloo tikki patty, Regular bun heel. The one that never goes out of f(l)avour.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Apple Slices. Fresh, crisp apple slices. A wholesome choice for any meal.. Fresh sliced apples. A fresh, healthy side.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "McEgg. Made with the freshest, warm, off-the-farm egg; steamed to perfection in our specialised steamer; and made tasty with a sprinkling of magic masala. Sandwiched between freshly toasted buns, topped off with\n                                creamy mayo and some crunchy onion.. Regular bun crown, Mayonnaise, Crisp onion, Egg, Curry spices, Regular bun heel. Because eggs are great any time of the day.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Mozzarella Sticks. Breaded mozzarella sticks served with marinara sauce for dipping.. Mozzarella cheese, breading, marinara dipping sauce. Cheesy fried snack.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sundae (Chocolate). Creamy vanilla soft-serve topped with thick and rich hot fudge.. Soft serve mix (100% diary), Hot fudge topping. Much more than ice-cream.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sundae (Chocolate). Creamy vanilla soft-serve topped with thick and rich hot fudge.. Soft serve mix (100% diary), Hot fudge topping. Much more than ice-cream.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Diet Coke. Small Diet Coke — crisp and refreshing.. Carbonated water, caramel color, aspartame, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. Zero-calorie cola.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Dosa Masala Burger. Turmeric-spiced mashed potato filling topped with fresh peas. Grilled and placed inside a soft whole wheat bun with a spicy molagapodi chutney mayo.. Whole wheat bun, Rasam mayo, Dosa masala aloo patty. A new taste of India.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Orange Juice. The McDonald's Minute Maid Orange Juice is 100% orange juice, loaded with Vitamin C. Available in small and medium sizes.. 100% orange juice from concentrate. Start your day with vitamin C.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Spicy Chicken Wrap. Juicy chicken coated with hot and crispy batter; dressed with a fresh salad of lettuce, onions, tomatoes and seasonings. Served with creamy sauce and supple cheese slices.. Whole wheat flat bread, Spicy chicken patty, Veg mayo, Lettuce, Onion, Tomato, Cheese. Familiar, yet different.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Double Quarter Pounder with Cheese. Two quarter pound 100% beef patties with two slices of cheese, pickles, onions, ketchup and mustard on a sesame seed bun.. Two quarter pound beef patties, two cheese slices, pickles, onions, ketchup, mustard, sesame bun. Serious beef appetite.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Strawberry Banana Smoothie. Blended strawberry and banana with creamy yogurt.. Strawberry puree, banana puree, low-fat yogurt, ice. Fruit smoothie treat.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Coca-Cola. Coca-Cola is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. The classic refreshment.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Coca-Cola. Coca-Cola is a refreshing McDonald's soda option that complements all of your menu favorites.. Carbonated water, high fructose corn syrup, caramel color, phosphoric acid, natural flavors, caffeine. The classic refreshment.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Our World Famous Fries. The crisp, craveable, fan favourite: our World Famous Fries. These epic fries are crispy and golden on the outside and fluffy on the inside.. Potato and salt. The legend among legends.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Fruit and Yogurt Parfait. Our creamy, low-fat vanilla yogurt layered with strawberries, blueberries and crunchy granola. A delicious snack or treat.. Low-fat vanilla yogurt, strawberries, blueberries, granola. A fresh, fruity treat.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sundae (Chocolate Brownie). An iconic premium dessert option. Can be bought as an add-on to make it a \"full meal\" or simply as an indulgence.. Soft serve mix (100% diary), Hazelnut brownie, Hot fudge topping. A global favourite.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Sundae (Chocolate Brownie). An iconic premium dessert option. Can be bought as an add-on to make it a \"full meal\" or simply as an indulgence.. Soft serve mix (100% diary), Hazelnut brownie, Hot fudge topping. A global favourite.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Pizza McPuff. A blend of assorted vegetables (carrot, beans,capsicum, onion & green peas); mozzarella cheese mixed with tomato sauce; and exotic spices stuffed in rectangle shaped savoury dough. Quick frozen.. Assorted vegetables, Refined wheat flour, Pizza seasoning. Something different. Something delicious.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Spicy Crispy Chicken Sandwich. A southern style fried chicken sandwich with a spicy pepper sauce. It's crispy, juicy, tender and topped with crinkle-cut pickles on a toasted, buttered potato roll.. Spicy crispy chicken fillet, crinkle-cut pickles, spicy pepper sauce, potato roll. Crispy chicken with a kick.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last.",
  [dialog 6/8]   |     "Chicken McNuggets. Bite-sized pieces of breaded, boneless chicken formed in various shapes (Ball, Boot, Bell & Bone) fried and served hot with smoky Barbeque Sauce or Mustard Sauce.. Chicken bites. Each bite is better than the last."
  [dialog 6/8]   |   ]
